New Avengers (001 - 020) (2013 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Zone-Empire) 


A Marvel NOW! title. To prevent the collision of our Universe with others, the Illuminati, led by Black Panther, must assemble NOW! It's the most powerful and brilliant team in the Marvel Universe -- Black Panther, Iron Man, Doctor Strange, Black Bolt, Mister Fantastic, Namor and Beast -- against an infinite legion of parallel realities.
